Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Did you hear about it?{Have you heard the gossip already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,And have you seen it?{And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Those two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,Overflowing with startling romance{A shockingly overflowing romance}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,All-consuming{The hottest topic now}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,Inescapable{It's all about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.31,Default,,0,0,20,,With a Taishou Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.07,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,Hi, Hi, Hi, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Having found out that it was the evil Lt Col Innen who orchestrated Shinobu's transfer to Kyushu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,High Collar Lady loses it. Her sight is set on the Imperial Army 1st Division Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The news reaches Kichiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,who also arrives at the site with an army of helpers, \Nnamely the Kanto Lilac Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,War makes strange bedfellows, {actually not a single clue what a single word of this could be}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,thus, even the nagging teacher decides to personally lead her students into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention Nanny, \Nwho joins the supporting army as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But we ought not to forget \Nabout one more important character:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's none other than the indomitable count, \Ndetermined to test the military's mettle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite that, our High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:02:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,resolves to storm the place on her own so no one else comes to harm.
