Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Hello! \NHanamura Benio has just arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Innen, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Hanamura Benio and\NI need to speak with Lt Col Innen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go inform him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are? Hey, if you want a meeting, \Napply for one in writing like everyone else!
