Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:33.57,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3735CF&\3c&HD9DFDB&}Sile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:33.74,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3735CF&\3c&HD9DFDB&}Silen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:34.37,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3735CF&\3c&HD9DFDB&}Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:46.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0B0301&\3c&HE8DBDC&\pos(1120,340.44)}I've lost
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, Innen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, civilian! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.14,Top,,0,0,0,,I told you to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.19,Top,,0,0,0,,Innen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.11,Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.25,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2E3552&\3c&HE0E0E0&\pos(851.56,647.11)}Visitors Reception {面会人受付}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.00,Top,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to have a meeting, you need to write your name and your address on this visitors' register.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My name and address? \NI don't have time for formalities!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This should suffice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
