Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lieutenant Colonel​... I-Innen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You've got a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trembling \Nover a simple visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You see, it's a schoolgirl \Nnamed Hanamura Benio and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hanamura Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura Benio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's right there, Lieutenant Colonel​.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Innen! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Hanamura...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one can start!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Next one step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, Innen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with her...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uhm, I-I....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tell her I'm not here! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, didn't you just say \Nthat she's a simple visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!\NNot in her case!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, tell her I'm away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Innen?\NHanamura Benio's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Innen! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap, Division Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no business with you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You, lady. Do you need anything here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well... uh..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to meet Lieutenant Colonel​ \NInnen face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?\NUh-uh, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God... Buddha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's this way. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the frying pan, into the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's your business \Nwith Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Uh-uh...\N"Alright..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's just a bad habit of mine. {/stock phrase}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pay no mind.\NUh-uh, oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what about some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, do you make tea yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, your own tea is the best\Nfor when you need to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I also have
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee, black tea, cocoa, \Ncoarse tea and green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:57.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\q2\c&H092250&\3c&HD5CFB9&\pos(736,140)}\h                           Coffee                           \h \N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\3c&HE6E6E7&}\h                                                               Candies  \N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\c&H0F0F21&\3c&H9A8889&}Tea                                                                                         \h \N\N\N\N{\3c&H8279C8&}Sweets {菓子}                      \h
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you could ever wish for, uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'd like some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh, alright, but you'll have to wait \Nwhile I make some great coffee for you, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to be spoiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That broad is something else! \NShe just waltzed in and attacked a military base!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's​ Innen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that bastard's face! {not really}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was your business \Nwith Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen? Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... You seem like a reasonable person, \Nso I guess I can tell you. {nc what hanasusou means here}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm. Feel free to tell me, uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. Where do I start...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like this is taking a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What might have happened to Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose she has met the firing squad yet. {/I sure hope she's not been executed by firing}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the soldiers are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Shinobu! Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Platoon, at ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this commotion, Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, so Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen \Ndid such a thing? Uh-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I can't really blame him \Nfor holding a grudge against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but Shinobu had nothing to do with any of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I understand what you mean, uh-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So now he's being transferred all the way to Kyushu to answer for {\i1}my{\i0} mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it has already been decided, uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Already decided or not, I just can't back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to your superior! \NYour superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? This is the 1st Division commander, Oukouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.07,Top,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:29.26,Top,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Division commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A lieutenant general?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh... uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh, got it. See you later. Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You see... actually... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no. No... You forgot this. This! Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are, Second Lieutenant Ijuuin. \NI was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive my fiancée's disorderly conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she was just worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for a disciplinary action here. Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,While some shady meddling \Nobviously took place,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the personnel change \Nis already set in stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll go there, won't you,\NIjuuin? Uhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. You've got yourself a nice fiancée there,\Nmake sure to treasure her, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We have many officers in our great army, \Nbut in times of emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,they couldn't stop this one-woman army \Nfrom taking the place by storm. {very unsure, hope its "alone; by oneself", and about the meaning in general}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not every day that you see \Na girl so masculine, uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh... uh-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:14.78,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(800,0)\c&H272B2A&\3c&HE6DBDB&\frz337\pos(772,234)}The Imperial Army heads to Russia! \NThe time nears to announce dispatch of troops {皇軍ついに\Nいよいよ出兵宣言近し}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Army is going to Russia. The time is finally near to announce the dispatch of troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.46,Top,,0,0,0,,Breaking news, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1918, fearing that Russia \Nmight fall to communism,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan on August 2nd and the U.S. the day after, both declared that they would send troops to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, to Russia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the Great War ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japanese Army in particular \Nsaw this as an opportunity to advance northward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In their blind confidence, \Nthey repeatedly funneled in more troops. {/arbitrarily}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The masses were deeply concerned that their husbands and sons would be sent to actual battlefields.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That same day, Shinobu, \Nwho was about to be transferred to Kyushu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,had breakfast with his family one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be fine there, Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so worried that they might \Nsend you to Siberia too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! The Nagoya regiment will be the first to be dispatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you're the only child \Nof our family, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you to be so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, where might she be indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so nice of you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bird told us you're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your lovely fiancée we've all missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she should be here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio? Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, where might she have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:13:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worked before. {/gag}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Feeding time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get out of here, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.91,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1D2813&\3c&HE4E1DC&\pos(1209,376)}Tenmaru
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so comfortable here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's nowhere to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you as sure as you can be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we checked every corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's think of a place where Benio could go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anybody have any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!\NShe might be {\i1}there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:15:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Saddened with Shinobu leaving, Boss went drinking to drown her sorrows! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not entirely unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have another idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's drowning her sorrows \Nin anmitsu, not alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, it's alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, anmitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anmitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anmitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're both wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's somewhere completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She might not look like one, but \Ndeep down Benio is a tender-hearted girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's definitely offering a hundredfold prayer. {https://www.japanesewiki.com/Shinto/Hyaku-do%20Mairi.html}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she's the same person \Nwho kept a night vigil when I was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right.\NBut I'm thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be busy gathering stitches for a senninbari \Nto wish Shinobu well in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:49.83,Sign,,0,0,0,,Best of luck in your battles{武運長久}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Senninbari" is a stomach band stitched a thousand times by a thousand people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to wish the soldier a safe return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:16:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Benio barely has time for anything, when she has so much to do to ensure her husband's safe return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant, make sure to watch yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we're trying to find out. \NThere's not a trace of her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! N-now, of all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go out for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you barking, you two? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Benio?\NIt's dangerous up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have climbed so high. \NCome on down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But Shinobu, it's my fault \Nthat you're being transferred to Kyushu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind if I join you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,N-N-No! Don't, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anybody to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you crying, Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... I mean, it's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have always caused you so much trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never thought it would come to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough worrying about that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've chosen to spend my life with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm willing to face with you\Nany curveballs fate throws your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:17:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't joke like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've loved you ever since we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Kyushu isn't all that far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you shouldn't think that this reassignment is for the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When your school vacation starts, \Nmake sure to pay me a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, \NKyushu is famous for its alcohol, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuma-shochu, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)}Yes, yes! I'll visit for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at who's finally smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It suits a high collar lady like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, I call for a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? A truce?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, until you return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up on Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But for the time you're away, \NI call for a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And while you're away, \NI'll keep protecting Benio any way I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a promise between men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch yourself, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay safe, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, take care of my grandfather and grandmother while I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just them, \NTenmaru and Chimaru too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too embarrassed to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,even though I thought about it all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry for being so stubborn up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth is that I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try to come back as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be faithfully waiting for you..." {/will remain loyal to you until then}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, I've become quite\Nmature and womanly, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin Shinobu, banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, come back home safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you come home, \NI'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, stay safe any way you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that I want to be your wife, \Nfrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's often said that meeting inevitably leads to parting,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but who would've thought \Nthat it would happen so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise that even our brave High Collar Lady is shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.22,0:22:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Will today's tears give way to a smile tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,High Collar Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:51.36,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,1000)\bord1.999\shad4\pos(1054.999,765)\c&HE3D3CF&\4c&HDED6CE&\3c&H00686C&}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.19,0:22:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio tries to be feminine,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:23:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and learn to behave like a proper wife,\Nwhile waiting for Shinobu's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.95,0:23:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But unexpectedly, Shinobu is transferred from Kyushu straight to Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking that this could once again be the result \Nof Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen's meddling,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,our High Collar Lady starts to plan a new raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.10,0:23:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,See in the next episode of \N{\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady{\i0},
